Download and Install Docker Desktop

https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop

Add Docker compose file from student asset folder
docker-compose.yml 

Run below command to Docker redis File in docker
PS C:\Demo> docker-compose up --detach

Install Redis through Package manager chocolatey
https://chocolatey.org/

Open PowerShell and run the below command
Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))

Package Manager

window powershell Runn command
 choco install redis-64 --version=3.0.501

 Open Command Prompt - to Start Rediu Server 
 C:\Users\reach>redis-server

 Open Command Prompt
 PS C:\Demo> redis-cli

 Download and install Redily app
 https://www.softpedia.com/dyn-postdownload.php/39487f1e464c8882e69a2502934370e6/612cb8c9/3fdb2/4/1
